Definition: insurance on the life of the insured for a fixed amount at a definite premium that is paid each year in the same amount during the entire lifetime of the insured
Synonyms: ordinary_life_insurance, straight_life_insurance, life_insurance, insurance, on, the, life, of, insured, for, a, fixed, amount, at, definite, premium, that, is, paid, each, year, in, same, during, entire, lifetime
Category: noun.possession
